data.description: Are you looking for your forever home? This may be the one, come check out this 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath on 1.+ acres.  Home had a NEW metal roof and skirting install in 2021. You'll love spending time on the new back deck and the covered front porch. Back yard is completely fenced, has 2 drive through gates, a walk through gate and a RV hook up. There are 3 Sheds for all your storage needs and a 2 car-carport. Inside the home you can host any party and be confident you'll have more than enough room with the HUGE living room, dining room and family room. All bedrooms are very spacious with 3 of the 4 featuring WALK-IN CLOSETS.  Large kitchen with lots of cabinet space and island.  Don't let this home pass you BUY, make your appointment today!!
